        "rich_text_YdAC6r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Heading",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>Destination Wedding Jewelry Guide: Travel Tips & Style Advice for Brides</h1>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kgTenL": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Every woman dreams of a destination wedding, but the planning for the wedding needs to be different as well! Whether your vows are echoed on a sunlit beach, a royal court, a vineyard or under the stars, your wedding jewelry should move as gracefully as you do. The right destination wedding jewelry does not just sparkle, but carries the story of your forever with deeper meaning, matches the theme of your wedding and is comfortable. Here’s your complete guide to selecting, styling, and safeguarding your destination wedding accessories. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_fPzzP6": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Understanding Destination Wedding Jewelry",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Understanding Destination Wedding Jewelry</h2><p>A destination wedding means movement, changing climates, and multiple looks and wedding jewelry for bride needs to adapt to all three. These pieces need to embody elegance while being travel friendly, lightweight, and versatile. Choose bridal jewelry with tight clasps, secure prongs, and with minimal maintenance needs. We believe that every piece should be crafted keeping these in mind. Our jewelry pieces are timeless companions that are versatile for every look and embody a bride’s dream day! </p><p>Lucira Tip: Choose jewelry with smooth edges that add finesse to the bridal look while also being travel friendly. </p>",
            "custom_id": "understanding",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cTXbb9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Choose the Right Jewelry According To Your Venue",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Choose the Right Jewelry According To Your Venue</h2>",
            "custom_id": "choose",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_HiDrQU": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1.1.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Every destination carries a distinct mood, and your jewelry should echo it. Dainty diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/jewelry\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Jewellery\">jewellery</a> in white gold looks breathtaking in beach weddings, while heavy chokers are uncomfortable and sticky in humid climates. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_pVP8aG": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2.1_0da32c8b-f731-432a-bfb4-a94557a5112c.jpg",
            "text": "<p>At heritage venues and palaces, embrace grandeur with a statement <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-necklaces\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Necklace\">necklace</a>, such as a choker necklace and <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/dangles\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Dangling Earring\">dangling earrings</a>. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_EDfLL4": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3.1.jpg",
            "text": "<p>For a wedding in vineyards or a destination surrounded by scenic views of the nature, choose earthy gemstones or champagne toned <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-jewellery\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Jewellery\">lab grown diamond jewellery</a> such as delicate wedding <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-bracelets\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bracelet\">bracelet</a> with a green gemstone that would complement natural backgrounds beautifully.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "round-ovale-dangling-earrings",
              "azure-oval-diamond-chain-bracelet"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dfTGtf": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lucira Tip",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Lucira Tip: Always try your jewelry set indoors as well as in outdoor lighting before finalizing a look. Daytime ceremonies favour jewelry that sparkles under sunlight and candlelit evenings call for pieces that glow softly in warmth. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_77QwYW": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Travel Safely with Fine Jewelry",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Travel Safely with Fine Jewelry</h2>",
            "custom_id": "travel",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NgU4A3": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Jewelry_Tip_Care.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Your jewelry is both valuable and sentimental, so it deserves thoughtful care during travel. Use compact jewelry organizers with a soft velvet lining that protects your wedding jewelry set without using too much space. Check for separate compartments for necklaces and jewelry <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Earrings\">earrings</a> in the jewelry organizer to prevent tangling and scratching while travelling.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mbQ3YQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Lucira Tip: If you have planned a beach wedding, a zip-lock pouch with a silica gel pack keeps humidity at bay, making your jewelry look brand new on your big day! </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_iFNCj8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Common Jewelry Mistakes Brides Make at Destination Weddings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Common Jewelry Mistakes Brides Make at Destination Weddings</h2><p>Even the most polished and perfectionist brides can overlook small details that affect comfort or aesthetics.</p>",
            "custom_id": "mistakes",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_WVEpbN": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Sand_related.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Wedding jewelry is often styled thinking that it needs to be extravagant, more in quantity and size. However multiple bold pieces can overwhelm the look and feel uncomfortable in heat or humidity. Overaccessorizing on the big day is a common mistake that brides make perceiving that the wedding day requires you to step out of your comfort.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_aJfUem": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p> Style your fine bridal jewelry set to look elegant and complement your look, instead of overwhelming it. While packing this, do not do it in a rush. Tangled necklaces and misplaced <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/stud-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Stud Earrings\">stud earrings</a> are common panic points for brides due to last minute packing! Last but not the least, do not neglect cleaning your jewelry. While fine jewelry is crafted to last a lifetime, its shine can dull due to over-exposure to sunscreen, makeup or hairspray. </p><p>Lucira Tip: Choose one hero piece per look - either a statement wedding necklace or earrings for bride and let it lead the ensemble.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_TEaF4P": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Caring for Your Jewelry Amid Sun, Sand, and Sea",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Caring for Your Jewelry Amid Sun, Sand, and Sea</h2><p>Tropical weddings are enchanting but they can be harsh on delicate pieces. Saltwater, sunscreen, and humidity can wear down even premium metals and stones. While putting on jewelry, ensure that you put on the jewelry last after wearing the outfit to avoid discomfort and after applying makeup and perfumes to prevent over exposure. To avoid any damage to your earrings and necklace set, wipe your pieces gently with a soft cloth to wipe any moisture or dust settled on it after the ceremony. Store all your pieces separately to prevent friction and scratching. </p><p>Lucira Tip: For seaside ceremonies, diamond jewelry and pearls are the most ideal choice as they both resist tarnish shimmer beautifully under sunlight. <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaires\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Solitaires\">Solitaire</a> diamond jewelry has always been the most-wanted jewelry because it captures the beauty of the moment perfectly, making it as grand as the milestone! </p>",
            "custom_id": "care",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_UGhYfV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion</h2><p>A destination wedding is not just about a new place, it’s about carrying pieces of your heart across landscapes, cultures, and memories. The jewelry you choose for that journey should mirror this very spirit - radiant yet effortless, luxurious yet deeply personal. When you think of destination wedding jewelry, think beyond the sparkle, think of how it moves with you and adds grace without demanding attention. Choose diamond jewellery that sits comfortably yet elegantly on you, that feels light and doesn’t just reflect a trend. So, as you pack your trunks with outfits and dreams, remember to pack your jewelry with the same care. Wrap your memories in velvet pouches, let your diamonds rest safely in their cases, and carry with you the quiet promise of forever - one glimmering piece at a time. </p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
